Output assets/demo.gif

Require echo

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.75

Hide
Type "export PATH=/opt/homebrew/bin:$PATH"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "advisor status"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "advisor plan /Users/justinadams/Downloads/advisor"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
